      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/posts/arduino-unreal/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;slug: arduino-unreal&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;arduino--unreal&#34;&gt;Arduino &amp;amp; Unreal&lt;a href=&#34;#arduino--unreal&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;A plugin for controlling Arduino from Unreal Engine.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Clone the repository and place it inside your Unreal project folder.&#xA;&lt;a&#xA;    href=&#34;https://github.com/RVillani/UE4Duino&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;inline-flex items-center gap-1&#34;&#xA;  &gt;https://github.com/RVillani/UE4Duino&lt;svg class=&#34;h-3 w-3 flex-shrink-0&#34; id=&#34;external-link&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;path fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; d=&#34;M15 3h6v6m-11 5L21 3m-3 10v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;tutorial&#34;&gt;Tutorial&lt;a href=&#34;#tutorial&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Set the port number to match your Arduino&amp;rsquo;s port number.&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure&#xA;  class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34;&#xA;  data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;&#xA;    true&#xA;  &#34;&#xA;  data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;  data-image-width=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;  data-image-height=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;  data-image-src=&#34;https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByFo6qxSn.png&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByFo6qxSn.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByFo6qxSn.png&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Configure the USB port number for the connection.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&#xA;  class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34;&#xA;  data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;&#xA;    true&#xA;  &#34;&#xA;  data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;  data-image-width=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;  data-image-height=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;  data-image-src=&#34;https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByeLaclBn.png&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByeLaclBn.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByeLaclBn.png&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
